com.metreeca.tree.probes

Class Traverser<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.metreeca.tree.probes.Traverser<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the generated result value
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shape.Probe<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Inspector, Optimizer, Redactor

    public abstract class Traverser<V>
extends Object
implements Shape.Probe<V>
    Shape traverser.

    Generates a result by traversing shapes; concrete implementations:

    • must define probing methods for structural and logical shapes;
    • may override probing methods for annotations and constraints of interest;
    • may override the generic probing method, applied by default to annotations and constraints;
